    "biography": {
      "value": "<p>Frost-Ghouls are the flash-frozen dead of the Svellheim wastes — corpses animated by the unnatural cold of the Wight-Lord's domain. They move with terrible, lurching speed, their rime-coated claws raking through armour to freeze the flesh beneath. They are drawn instinctively to warmth, hunting by the faintest heat signature.</p>",
      "director": "<p>Frost-Ghouls are fast harriers — Speed 7 lets them close quickly. Use Heat-Seeker to gain edge against targets near fire or who used fire abilities. Lead with Frost-Rake to slow a target, then use Pounce (3 Malice) to shift into position and upgrade that slow to restrained. Fragile Dead means a 10+ damage single hit dazes them — avoid clustering them where AoE can catch multiple ghouls.</p>",
